{"tid":328362,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"[駕駛知識] 如何正確使用高燈","createTime":"2017-07-19T13:46:46.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-05T16:37:00.000Z","uid":44728,"like":18,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"9a76e512a6f730c4ca1c5e8a754e7a8dfc1f8836","tid":328362,"uid":44728,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T13:46:46.000Z","msg":"見到隔籬post討論緊啲人亂用高燈，特登cut咗條片出嚟 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=utk3IeStnxU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dutk3IeStnxU&d=CxJ8%2BFLYWbLSA8PXSumrPzA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=a15df7de\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=utk3IeStnxU</a><br />\n<br />\n只於完全漆黑環境中使用高燈。若遇對頭車則短暫轉回低燈，以免影響對方視綫。<br />\n<br />\n若跟隨前車，則無需使用高燈，因前車已照明，乖乖跟隨行駛就可以。"},{"pid":"764c312111e6aea2d39760b7b9bfc60dbe94714d","tid":328362,"uid":4517,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T14:01:44.000Z","msg":"喺香港基本上唔洗用，除非極大乳"},{"pid":"4e29d71838832033c42089b42b5921ae10f25bbe","tid":328362,"uid":9230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T14:10:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>喺香港基本上唔洗用，除非極大乳</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n極大雨，開霧燈"},{"pid":"eba7bd79cfe59cbd5921bf4924d1f321bad4d75e","tid":328362,"uid":73123,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T14:46:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>喺香港基本上唔洗用，除非極大乳</blockquote><br />\n極大雨已經睇唔到路，仲要俾你d高燈撚射到更加睇唔到野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9bce0450eedd6a40dbf0925eb2dcd138590dd18","tid":328362,"uid":4032,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T14:53:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>喺香港基本上唔洗用，除非極大乳</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n大雨都唔應該開高燈。大雨開燈係方便其他車見到自己架車，唔係用嚟照明睇路。高燈照住對面/前面司機對眼，影響其他人駕駛。"},{"pid":"560c40c1a02511ed045ddbc4d77cb70dcd4b5b68","tid":328362,"uid":4032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T14:59:30.000Z","msg":"二來啲傾盆大雨會反射返高燈啲光，結果司機仲加睇唔到路。"},{"pid":"659135f28f3e6b948942c57b80150036598da328","tid":328362,"uid":115451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T15:01:37.000Z","msg":"依家成日好殘眼果啲就高燈 可唔可以咁理解？"},{"pid":"afb4d2f105c147ebdc3564f960e606174186f800","tid":328362,"uid":11454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T15:03:05.000Z","msg":"高燈係俾冇街燈既山路/外國既高速公路用<br />\n同埋有對頭車要轉一轉番低燈<br />\n<br />\n香港真係好少會用到， 但總有d盲撚亂咁開， 又唔識睇高燈個藍色公仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b226a7433f4245262114b890076a998533a3f1c","tid":328362,"uid":18740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T15:04:27.000Z","msg":"讓你行先<br />\n<br />\n通常呢個先打"},{"pid":"982b5340426715f8c309ae525e9449447d728639","tid":328362,"uid":32470,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T15:06:21.000Z","msg":"挑機用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"989e6565ac72ed58c7c024e8a685a9775917ce69","tid":328362,"uid":100474,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T15:16:31.000Z","msg":"有啲傻鳩舊車要裝LED搞撚到冇大細燈之分"},{"pid":"59c6f44455b2386c1163e2b65714620e2f142aef","tid":328362,"uid":44728,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T15:57:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>依家成日好殘眼果啲就高燈 可唔可以咁理解？</blockquote><br />\n基本上係，因為低燈係唔應該殘眼的<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af590328c7437130b592ed8ec478cb997040b936","tid":328362,"uid":51052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T16:15:56.000Z","msg":"宜家香港變撚到大陸咁<br />\n好多車改撚到對頭車乜鳩都睇唔到"},{"pid":"21f4b9a61f8e13d63b791aab8b4db62944f6f698","tid":328362,"uid":44728,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T16:28:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>宜家香港變撚到大陸咁<br />\n好多車改撚到對頭車乜鳩都睇唔到</blockquote><br />\n嗰啲改到藍燈咁，就算唔殘眼都睇壞眼 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7f8d90d4c56d4a9ad55cb0b0ed553b1a7ebbe9f","tid":328362,"uid":122896,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T16:32:04.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/u761kLWdY8s\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fu761kLWdY8s&d=CxJ8%2BFLYWbLSA8PXSumrPzA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=9a1b6735\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/u761kLWdY8s</a>"},{"pid":"a044aa7d2e400c32b829fea8da1bfdc5d8de2b30","tid":328362,"uid":19542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T16:34:36.000Z","msg":"其實係啲車廠整到啲燈好q光<br />\nhigh beam low beam都好殘眼"},{"pid":"1593139a836a7a89a64950ceec960c440b2b519d","tid":328362,"uid":52215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T23:21:44.000Z","msg":"著高燈係咪錶板顯示藍色logo？"},{"pid":"f00f0238ab8d56b6dd1dbdda34480321774e75b8","tid":328362,"uid":37717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T23:26:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>著高燈係咪錶板顯示藍色logo？</blockquote><br />\n正確無誤<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2f2cabd497b6b80b913073987ffc6c9f7419201","tid":328362,"uid":33004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T23:36:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實係啲車廠整到啲燈好q光<br />\nhigh beam low beam都好殘眼</blockquote><br />\nAgger <br />\n唔知香港既新Lexus 係咪一樣<br />\n係美國d Lexus 真係射撚到人眼盲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好鬼憎揸Lexus 前面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"193a4e3a3cf5377a7223611e21406b07281e2b33","tid":328362,"uid":44728,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T11:41:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af505bbb6eeb5df78a16f3b7f7ef45494b6394c1","tid":328362,"